    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"final punctuation mark\" thing... it's a weirdly comforting thought. Most people tell me I have so much more to see, but they don't get it. It's like the trip was great, but now the luggage is just too heavy to keep carrying around. I'm just so incredibly tired of the journey. Do you think it's wrong to just want to reach the destination and be done with the travel?",
